When power meets perfection! We were honoured to welcome @tehseenpoonawalla — entrepreneur, political voice, and style icon — to SOHNAA’s showcase at the Pune exhibition. His admiration for our collection was a true moment of pride.

SOHNAA, a luxury jewellery house rooted in heritage and driven by design, brings together timeless artistry and modern elegance. Seeing our pieces appreciated by someone known for both intellect and impeccable taste makes this memory even more special.

Thank you, Tehseen, for your gracious presence and inspiring words!

Sohnaa (@livesohnaa ) is a fine jewelry brand that beautifully blends cultural heritage with modern minimalism. Founded by the talented and award-winning designer Sonali Shah Sheth (@sonalishahsheth ), her dedication and tenacity shine through every creation. With a refreshing palette and distinctive styles, Sohnaa’s pieces are a fun yet sophisticated addition to any look.

Nominated among the top 18 luxury startups worldwide at the Luxury Innovation Summit in Geneva, the brand is celebrated for its effortless ability to transition between traditional and modern aesthetics. #SohnaaJewelry #TimelessLuxury #ModernHeritage
